Interleukin-18 (IL-18) plays a role in the host's response to tumours and 
angiogenesis. We determined serum levels of IL-18, vascular endothelial growth 
factor (VEGF), angiogenin (ANG), tumor necrosis factor (TNF-alpha) and CRP in 65 
